  p Hello #{firstName},

  p Your document request has been <strong>cancelled</strong>.

  p
    strong Document Type:
    |  #{documentType}

  p
    strong Reason:
    |  #{cancelReason}

  p You may view the request details or submit a new request using the button below.

  table.btn.btn-primary(role='presentation', border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0')
    tbody
      tr
        td(align='left')
          table(role='presentation', border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0')
            tbody
              tr
                td
                  a(href=`${url}`, target='_blank') View Request

